{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":294,"text":"I've spent my life working on sustainability."},{"time":3047,"text":"I set up a climate change NGO"},{"time":5102,"text":"called The Climate Group."},{"time":6422,"text":"I worked on forestry issues in WWF."},{"time":9813,"text":"I worked on development and agriculture issues"},{"time":11889,"text":"in the U.N. system."},{"time":13624,"text":"About 25 years in total,"},{"time":15548,"text":"and then three years ago, I found myself talking to"},{"time":18271,"text":"IKEA's CEO about joining his team."},{"time":21556,"text":"Like many people here, well,"},{"time":23582,"text":"I want to maximize my personal impact in the world,"},{"time":27517,"text":"so I'm going to explain why I joined the team there."}]},{"cues":[{"time":32203,"text":"But first, let's just take three numbers."}]},{"cues":[{"time":35010,"text":"The first number is three:"},{"time":37081,"text":"three billion people."},{"time":38641,"text":"This is the number of people joining"},{"time":40452,"text":"the global middle class by 2030,"},{"time":42504,"text":"coming out of poverty."},{"time":43813,"text":"It's fantastic for them and their families,"},{"time":46054,"text":"but we've got two billion people in the global middle class today,"},{"time":49097,"text":"and this swells that number to five,"},{"time":51394,"text":"a big challenge when we already have resource scarcity."}]},{"cues":[{"time":54724,"text":"The second number is six:"},{"time":56601,"text":"This is six degrees centigrade,"},{"time":58746,"text":"what we're heading towards in terms of global warming."},{"time":61310,"text":"We're not heading towards one degree or three degrees"},{"time":63361,"text":"or four degrees, we're heading toward six degrees."},{"time":65709,"text":"And if you think about it, all of the weird weather"},{"time":68398,"text":"we've been having the last few years,"},{"time":70241,"text":"much of that is due to just one degree warming,"},{"time":72823,"text":"and we need CO2 emissions to peak"},{"time":75118,"text":"by the end of this decade globally"},{"time":77350,"text":"and then come down."},{"time":79078,"text":"It's not inevitable, but we need to act decisively."}]},{"cues":[{"time":83149,"text":"The third number is 12:"},{"time":84910,"text":"That's the number of cities in the world"},{"time":86403,"text":"that had a million or more people"},{"time":88194,"text":"when my grandmother was born."},{"time":89627,"text":"You can see my grandmother there."},{"time":91247,"text":"That was in the beginning of the last century."},{"time":93290,"text":"So just 12 cities. She was born in Manchester, England,"},{"time":95306,"text":"the ninth largest city in the world."},{"time":97327,"text":"Now there are 500 cities, nearly,"},{"time":100032,"text":"with a million people or more in them."},{"time":102463,"text":"And if you look at the century from 1950 to 2050,"},{"time":105807,"text":"that's the century when we build all the world's cities,"},{"time":109551,"text":"the century that we're in the middle of right now."},{"time":111961,"text":"Every other century was kind of practice,"},{"time":114807,"text":"and this lays down a blueprint for how we live."}]},{"cues":[{"time":119625,"text":"So think about it."},{"time":121380,"text":"We're building cities like never before,"},{"time":124150,"text":"bringing people out of poverty like never before,"},{"time":126676,"text":"and changing the climate like never before."},{"time":129051,"text":"Sustainability has gone from a nice-to-do"},{"time":132111,"text":"to a must-do."},{"time":133776,"text":"it's about what we do right here, right now,"},{"time":136609,"text":"and for the rest of our working lives."}]},{"cues":[{"time":140290,"text":"So I'm going to talk a little bit about"},{"time":142322,"text":"what business can do"},{"time":143695,"text":"and what a business like IKEA can do,"},{"time":145997,"text":"and we have a sustainability strategy"},{"time":148664,"text":"called \"people and planet positive\""},{"time":150661,"text":"to help guide our business to have a positive impact on the world."},{"time":154308,"text":"Why would we not want to have a positive impact"},{"time":156443,"text":"on the world as a business?"},{"time":159031,"text":"Other companies have sustainability strategies."},{"time":161519,"text":"I'm going to refer to some of those as well,"},{"time":163357,"text":"and I'm just going to mention a few"},{"time":164894,"text":"of the commitments as illustrations that we've got."}]},{"cues":[{"time":167490,"text":"But first, let's think of customers."},{"time":169506,"text":"We know from asking people from China to the U.S."},{"time":173331,"text":"that the vast majority of people care about sustainability"},{"time":176659,"text":"after the day-to-day issues,"},{"time":178541,"text":"the day-to-day issues of, how do I get my kids to school?"},{"time":181118,"text":"Can I pay the bills at the end of the month?"},{"time":183097,"text":"Then they care about big issues like climate change."},{"time":186559,"text":"But they want it to be easy, affordable and attractive,"},{"time":190991,"text":"and they expect business to help,"},{"time":192983,"text":"and they're a little bit disappointed today."}]},{"cues":[{"time":195777,"text":"So take your mind back and think"},{"time":198411,"text":"of the first sustainable products."},{"time":199998,"text":"We had detergents that could wash your whites grayer."},{"time":203911,"text":"We had the early energy-efficient light bulbs"},{"time":206965,"text":"that took five minutes to warm up"},{"time":208812,"text":"and then you were left looking a kind of sickly color."},{"time":211883,"text":"And we had the rough, recycled toilet paper."},{"time":215251,"text":"So every time you pulled on a t-shirt,"},{"time":217983,"text":"or switched the light on, or went to the bathroom,"},{"time":220089,"text":"or sometimes all three together,"},{"time":221758,"text":"you were reminded sustainability was about compromise."},{"time":225203,"text":"It wasn't a great start."}]},{"cues":[{"time":228101,"text":"Today we have choices."},{"time":230389,"text":"We can make products that are beautiful or ugly,"},{"time":233686,"text":"sustainable or unsustainable, affordable or expensive,"},{"time":238487,"text":"functional or useless."},{"time":240350,"text":"So let's make beautiful, functional, affordable,"},{"time":243215,"text":"sustainable products."}]},{"cues":[{"time":245535,"text":"Let's take the LED."},{"time":247831,"text":"The LED is the next best thing to daylight."},{"time":251245,"text":"The old-fashioned lightbulbs, the incandescent bulbs --"},{"time":254426,"text":"I'm not going to ask for a show of hands"},{"time":255934,"text":"of how many of you still have them in your homes,"},{"time":258223,"text":"wasting energy every time you switch them on --"},{"time":261045,"text":"change them after this --"},{"time":262482,"text":"or whether we have them on the stage here at TED or not --"},{"time":266175,"text":"but those old incandescent light bulbs"},{"time":269966,"text":"really should have been sold as heaters."},{"time":272988,"text":"They were mis-sold for more than a hundred years."},{"time":274965,"text":"They produced heat and a little bit of light on the side."},{"time":277407,"text":"Now we have lights that produce light"},{"time":279479,"text":"and a little bit of heat on the side."},{"time":281171,"text":"You save 85 percent of the electricity with an LED"},{"time":283997,"text":"that you would have done in an old incandescent."},{"time":286040,"text":"And the best thing is, they'll also last"},{"time":287775,"text":"for more than 20 years."},{"time":289354,"text":"So think about that."},{"time":290610,"text":"You'll change your smartphone seven or eight times,"},{"time":293106,"text":"probably more if you're in this audience."},{"time":295182,"text":"You'll change your car, if you have one, three or four times."},{"time":297792,"text":"Your kids could go to school, go to college,"},{"time":300344,"text":"go away and have kids of their own, come back,"},{"time":302299,"text":"bring the grandkids,"},{"time":303725,"text":"you'll have the same lightbulb saving you energy."},{"time":307611,"text":"So LEDs are fantastic."},{"time":310450,"text":"What we decided to do"},{"time":311976,"text":"was not to sell LEDs on the side marked up high"},{"time":314929,"text":"and continue to push all the old bulbs,"},{"time":317155,"text":"the halogens and the CFLs."},{"time":319146,"text":"We decided, over the next two years,"},{"time":322076,"text":"we will ban the halogens and the CFLs ourselves."},{"time":324591,"text":"We will go all in."},{"time":325959,"text":"And this is what business needs to do: go all-in,"},{"time":327668,"text":"go 100 percent,"},{"time":329112,"text":"because then you stop investing in the old stuff,"},{"time":330703,"text":"you invest in the new stuff, you lower costs,"},{"time":332857,"text":"you use your supply chain and your creativity"},{"time":335186,"text":"and you get the prices down so everybody can afford"},{"time":337943,"text":"the best lights so they can save energy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":340894,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":345044,"text":"It's not just about products in people's homes."},{"time":348173,"text":"We've got to think about the raw materials"},{"time":349817,"text":"that produce our products."},{"time":351999,"text":"Obviously there's fantastic opportunities"},{"time":353826,"text":"with recycled materials,"},{"time":355320,"text":"and we can and will go zero waste."},{"time":358163,"text":"And there's opportunities in a circular economy."},{"time":360151,"text":"But we're still dependent on natural, raw materials."},{"time":363593,"text":"Let's take cotton."},{"time":365383,"text":"Cotton's brilliant. Probably many people"},{"time":367112,"text":"are wearing cotton right now."},{"time":368523,"text":"It's a brilliant textile in use."},{"time":370057,"text":"It's really dirty in production."},{"time":371624,"text":"It uses lots of pesticides, lots of fertilizer, lots of water."},{"time":375758,"text":"So we've worked with others,"},{"time":377378,"text":"with other businesses and NGOs,"},{"time":378980,"text":"on the Better Cotton Initiative,"},{"time":380836,"text":"working right back down to the farm,"},{"time":383005,"text":"and there you can halve the amount of water"},{"time":384840,"text":"and halve the chemical inputs,"},{"time":386671,"text":"the yields increase, and 60 percent of the costs"},{"time":389567,"text":"of running many of these farms"},{"time":391236,"text":"with farmers with low incomes"},{"time":393280,"text":"can be chemical imports."},{"time":394983,"text":"Yields increase, and you halve the input costs."},{"time":397128,"text":"Farmers are coming out of poverty. They love it."},{"time":400003,"text":"Already hundreds of thousands of farmers"},{"time":401730,"text":"have been reached,"},{"time":403320,"text":"and now we've got 60 percent better cotton in our business."},{"time":405984,"text":"Again, we're going all-in."},{"time":407326,"text":"By 2015, we'll be 100 percent Better Cotton."}]},{"cues":[{"time":410476,"text":"Take the topic of 100 percent targets, actually."},{"time":413462,"text":"People sometimes think that"},{"time":415134,"text":"100 percent's going to be hard,"},{"time":416599,"text":"and we've had the conversation in the business."},{"time":418370,"text":"Actually, we found 100 percent is easier to do"},{"time":420212,"text":"than 90 percent or 50 percent."},{"time":422199,"text":"If you have a 90 percent target,"},{"time":423631,"text":"everyone in the business finds a reason"},{"time":425052,"text":"to be in the 10 percent."},{"time":426857,"text":"When it's 100 percent, it's kind of clear,"},{"time":430427,"text":"and businesspeople like clarity,"},{"time":433317,"text":"because then you just get the job done."}]},{"cues":[{"time":435982,"text":"So, wood. We know with forestry, it's a choice."},{"time":438730,"text":"You've got illegal logging"},{"time":440324,"text":"and deforestation still on a very large scale,"},{"time":443149,"text":"or you can have fantastic, responsible forestry"},{"time":445849,"text":"that we can be proud of."},{"time":447984,"text":"It's a simple choice, so we've worked"},{"time":450066,"text":"for many years with the Forest Stewardship Council,"},{"time":452610,"text":"with literally hundreds of other organizations,"},{"time":454980,"text":"and there's a point here about collaboration."},{"time":457420,"text":"So hundreds of others, of NGOs,"},{"time":459315,"text":"of forest workers' unions, and of businesses,"},{"time":461897,"text":"have helped create the Forest Stewardship Council,"},{"time":463569,"text":"which sets standards for forestry"},{"time":465351,"text":"and then checks the forestry's good on the ground."},{"time":467873,"text":"Now together, through our supply chain,"},{"time":470116,"text":"with partners, we've managed to certify"},{"time":471983,"text":"35 million hectares of forestry."},{"time":474860,"text":"That's about the size of Germany."},{"time":477397,"text":"And we've decided in the next three years,"},{"time":479185,"text":"we will double the volume of certified material"},{"time":481220,"text":"we put through our business."},{"time":483358,"text":"So be decisive on these issues."},{"time":485998,"text":"Use your supply chain to drive good."}]},{"cues":[{"time":487969,"text":"But then it comes to your operations."},{"time":489995,"text":"Some things are certain, I think."},{"time":492645,"text":"We know we'll use electricity in 20 or 30 years' time."},{"time":495660,"text":"We know the sun will be shining somewhere,"},{"time":498583,"text":"and the wind will still be blowing in 20 or 30 years' time."},{"time":501675,"text":"So why not make our energy out of the sun and the wind?"},{"time":504327,"text":"And why not take control of it ourselves?"},{"time":506555,"text":"So we're going 100 percent renewable."},{"time":508915,"text":"By 2020, we'll produce more renewable energy"},{"time":511671,"text":"than the energy we consume as a business."},{"time":513691,"text":"For all of our stores, our own factories,"},{"time":515667,"text":"our distribution centers,"},{"time":517045,"text":"we've installed 300,000 solar panels so far,"},{"time":519499,"text":"and we've got 14 wind farms we own and operate"},{"time":522873,"text":"in six countries, and we're not done yet."},{"time":525500,"text":"But think of a solar panel."},{"time":527284,"text":"A solar panel pays for itself in seven or eight years."},{"time":529463,"text":"The electricity is free."},{"time":530956,"text":"Every time the sun comes out after that,"},{"time":532761,"text":"the electricity is free."},{"time":534196,"text":"So this is a good thing for the CFO,"},{"time":536213,"text":"not just the sustainability guy."},{"time":538156,"text":"Every business can do things like this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":541190,"text":"But then we've got to look beyond our operations,"},{"time":544169,"text":"and I think everybody would agree"},{"time":545918,"text":"that now business has to take full responsibility"},{"time":548290,"text":"for the impacts of your supply chain."},{"time":550494,"text":"Many businesses now, fortunately,"},{"time":552810,"text":"have codes of conduct and audit their supply chains,"},{"time":554817,"text":"but not every business. Far from it."},{"time":556863,"text":"And this came in IKEA actually in the '90s."},{"time":559377,"text":"We found there was a risk"},{"time":561118,"text":"of child labor in the supply chain,"},{"time":563120,"text":"and people in the business were shocked."},{"time":565630,"text":"And it was clearly totally unacceptable, so then you have to act."},{"time":568954,"text":"So a code of conduct was developed,"},{"time":571098,"text":"and now we have 80 auditors out in the world"},{"time":574049,"text":"every day making sure all our factories"},{"time":576080,"text":"secure good working conditions"},{"time":578364,"text":"and protect human rights"},{"time":579913,"text":"and make sure there is no child labor."}]},{"cues":[{"time":582174,"text":"But it's not just as simple as making sure"},{"time":584334,"text":"there's no child labor."},{"time":586366,"text":"You've got to say that's not enough today."},{"time":588566,"text":"I think we'd all agree that children"},{"time":590614,"text":"are the most important people in the world"},{"time":592810,"text":"and the most vulnerable."},{"time":594707,"text":"So what can a business do today"},{"time":596955,"text":"to actually use your total value chain"},{"time":598839,"text":"to support a better quality of life"},{"time":601118,"text":"and protect child rights?"},{"time":602706,"text":"We've worked with UNICEF and Save the Children"},{"time":605003,"text":"on developing some new business principles"},{"time":607478,"text":"with children's rights."},{"time":608943,"text":"Increasing numbers of businesses"},{"time":610760,"text":"are signing up to these,"},{"time":612280,"text":"but actually in a survey, many business leaders"},{"time":614743,"text":"said they thought their business had nothing to do with children."},{"time":617610,"text":"So what we decided to do was, we will look"},{"time":621109,"text":"and ask ourselves the tough questions"},{"time":622670,"text":"with partners who know more than us,"},{"time":624734,"text":"what can we do to go beyond our business"},{"time":627691,"text":"to help improve the lives of children?"},{"time":629533,"text":"We also have a foundation"},{"time":631352,"text":"that's committed to work through partners"},{"time":633247,"text":"and help improve the lives and protect the rights"},{"time":635870,"text":"of 100 million children by 2015."}]},{"cues":[{"time":638737,"text":"You know the phrase,"},{"time":640413,"text":"you can manage what you measure?"},{"time":643791,"text":"Well, you should measure what you care about."},{"time":648441,"text":"If you're not measuring things,"},{"time":649990,"text":"you don't care and you don't know."},{"time":652734,"text":"So let's take an example, measure the things"},{"time":654903,"text":"that are important in your business."},{"time":657060,"text":"Isn't it about time that businesses"},{"time":659343,"text":"were led equally by men and women?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":662321,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":665304,"text":"So we know for our 17,000 managers across IKEA"},{"time":670446,"text":"that 47 percent are women today,"},{"time":673410,"text":"but it's not enough, and we want to close the gap"},{"time":675806,"text":"and follow it all the way through to senior management."},{"time":678093,"text":"And we do not want to wait another hundred years."},{"time":680939,"text":"So we've launched a women's open network"},{"time":683898,"text":"this week in IKEA,"},{"time":685423,"text":"and we'll do whatever it takes to lead the change."},{"time":687599,"text":"So the message here is,"},{"time":689014,"text":"measure what you care about and lead the change,"},{"time":691398,"text":"and don't wait a hundred years."}]},{"cues":[{"time":694401,"text":"So we've gone from sustainability"},{"time":696838,"text":"being a nice-to-do to a must-do. It's a must-do."},{"time":702074,"text":"It's still nice to do, but it's a must-do."},{"time":705226,"text":"And everybody can do something on this as an individual."},{"time":710161,"text":"Be a discerning consumer."},{"time":712357,"text":"Vote with your wallets."},{"time":714055,"text":"Search out the companies"},{"time":716235,"text":"that are acting on this."},{"time":718930,"text":"But also, there are other businesses already acting."},{"time":721977,"text":"I mentioned renewable energy."},{"time":724122,"text":"You go to Google or Lego,"},{"time":726440,"text":"they're going 100 percent renewable too,"},{"time":728700,"text":"in the same way that we are."},{"time":730067,"text":"On having really good sustainability strategies,"},{"time":733193,"text":"there are companies like Nike, Patagonia,"},{"time":736437,"text":"Timberland, Marks &amp; Spencer."},{"time":738591,"text":"But I don't think any of those businesses would say"},{"time":740749,"text":"they're perfect. We certainly wouldn't."},{"time":743014,"text":"We'll make mistakes going forward,"},{"time":745380,"text":"but it's about setting a clear direction, being transparent,"},{"time":747897,"text":"having a dialogue with the right partners,"},{"time":749586,"text":"and choosing to lead on the issues that really count."}]},{"cues":[{"time":754102,"text":"So if you're a business leader,"},{"time":756901,"text":"if you're not already weaving sustainability"},{"time":759856,"text":"right into the heart of your business model,"},{"time":762264,"text":"I'd urge you to do so."},{"time":764155,"text":"And together, we can help create"},{"time":766130,"text":"a sustainable world,"},{"time":768130,"text":"and, if we get it right,"},{"time":770259,"text":"we can make sustainability"},{"time":771748,"text":"affordable for the many people,"},{"time":773370,"text":"not a luxury for the few."}]},{"cues":[{"time":775067,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":776424,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}